Package de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.datastructures

Basic memory structures such as heaps and object hierarchies.

See: Description


  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnyMap<K>
    Associative storage based on a HashMap for multiple object types that offers a type checked AnyMap.get(Object, Class) method.
    HashMapList<K,V>
    Multi-Associative container, that stores a list of values for a particular key.
    MaskedArrayList<T>
    This class is a virtual collection based on masking an array list using a bit mask.
    QuickSelect
    QuickSelect computes ("selects") the element at a given rank and can be used to compute Medians and arbitrary quantiles by computing the appropriate rank.
